      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<i></i><a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeslieforColorado/"><img src="https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/cp0/p50x50/46110182_2103163249735231_8400532839258390528_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=dbb9e7&_nc_ohc=pcI0YVaINTYAX__IAaw&_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna&_nc_tp=27&oh=8b4f40cc02eeabc19e76fb9c167a11d6&oe=5FA8B611" alt="" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeslieforColorado/">Representative Leslie Herod<a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeslieforColorado/"></a></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeslieforColorado/posts/2206768966041325"></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com"><i></i></a><p>Incredibly humbled by this feature in 5280 and honored to have community support for this work. We all have a story to tell. Our stories are our strength and our voices will be heard.</p><p> "Forget political stereotypes: This history-making legislator is unapologetically progressive, is insistent that state government can be bipartisan (even now), and wants to transform the criminal justice system. And that's just the start of her ambitions.”</p><p> - <a href="https://www.facebook.com/5280Magazine/">5280 Magazine</a></p>...<p> 📸 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pauljmillerphotography/">Paul Miller Photography</a><br /> Hair: Dornise LaTone Afhair<br /> Styling: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/LilFreshSamFanpage/">LILFRESHSAM</a></p> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeslieforColorado/posts/2206768966041325">See More</a><a href="https://www.5280.com/2019/01/state-representative-leslie-herod-has-a-story-to-share/?fbclid=IwAR3W3UTd8Ztzpb1mlTprtBaljUpq-2NMV9xKfNKQ5kCPT5-3BQI0_zEPcpE">Forget political stereotypes: This history-making legislator is unapologetically progressive, is insistent that state government can be bipartisan (even now), and wants to transform the criminal justice system. And that's just the start of her ambitions.<img src="https://external.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQBDqixwaA1vynHY&w=540&h=282&url=https%3A%2F%2Fs22409.pcdn.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FLeslie-Herod-closeup_Paul-Miller.jpg&cfs=1&upscale=1&fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&_nc_cb=1&_nc_hash=AQB1BD0eY1iiM21l" alt="" width="500" height="262" caption="" /></a><p>5280.com</p><p>State Representative Leslie Herod Has a Story to Share | 5280</p>Forget political stereotypes: This history-making legislator is unapologetically progressive, is insistent that state government can be bipartisan (even now), and wants to transform the criminal justice system. And that's just the start of her ambitions.<a href="https://www.5280.com/2019/01/state-representative-leslie-herod-has-a-story-to-share/?fbclid=IwAR3W3UTd8Ztzpb1mlTprtBaljUpq-2NMV9xKfNKQ5kCPT5-3BQI0_zEPcpE">Forget political stereotypes: This history-making legislator is unapologetically progressive, is insistent that state government can be bipartisan (even now), and wants to transform the criminal justice system. And that's just the start of her ambitions.</a>]]></content:encoded>
